@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Note
# Florence-2 로컬 태거로 ingest를 먼저 실행한 뒤 검색해야 결과가 나온다.

### Tag Search
POST {{baseUrl}}/search/by-tags
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "query": "사과",
  "top_k": 5
}

### Deprecated Alias
POST {{baseUrl}}/search/text
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "query": "apple",
  "top_k": 3
}
